  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[When Digivolving] Delete up to 7 play cost's total worth
    of your opponent's Digimon. [Opponent's Turn] All of your Digimon with the [D-Brigade]
    trait gain \uFF1CBlocker\uFF1E. [End of Your Turn][Once Per Turn] Reveal the
    top 3 cards of your deck. You may play up to 7 play cost's total worth of cards
    with the [D-Brigade] or [DigiPolice] trait among them without paying the costs.
    Trash the rest."
